subject: Soccer
lead_paragraph: Everton rallied past Middlesbrough, 2-1, on Sunday to set up an F.A. Cup semifinal against Manchester United in April at Wembley. Arsenal defeated the lower-tier club Burnley, 3-0, to reach the quarterfinals. Held up by postponements and replays, Arsenal will face Hull in a quarterfinal. The winner will play Chelsea in the semifinals.
